Text: This is about my home country Pakistan, when I was eighteen years old. Friends
  make up a plan for fairy meadows trip with small budget but that place which I've
  seen there is out of world I means I never that this is in Pakistan my Pakistan.
  It's looks like Switzerland at all. I one of my friend told me that this is the
  world highest battle field & I replied him this place is not for battle infact it's
  for the inner peace & harmony. We stayed at there for 2 nights & 3 days. The peace
  in the sleep of night, the shine of moon always gives me the perfect line for my
  poetry. The morning breezes gives me the smell of heaven & the sun shine feela like
  the perfect harm feels that I need at the moment. This was
